This would allow the EU to contribute to and utilize the capabilities of NATO's integrated military command in a manner that strengthens NATO's European pillar, rather than building an alternative capability outside of NATO. NATO's top military commander (SACEUR) is an American, but his deputy (DSACEUR) is always a European.
